Resident Evil 5
{{achtung|CHRIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIS}}
[[Image:re5.jpg|thumb|right|Finally! A game that does what we're all thinking! Pool's CLOSED]]

'''''Resident Evil 5''''' (otherwise known as "PUNCH NIGGERS RECEIVE CAKE") is the fifteenth game in the ''Resident Evil'' series.  It was released for the [[Xbox 360|Tre Shitty]] and some other [[Playstation 3|really expensive thing]].  The only thing that distinguishes this game from the fourteen that come before it is (except [[Resident Evil 4|number fourteen itself]]), instead of killing [[zombies]], you walk around [[Africa]] endlessly shooting entire villages of pissed off mutant [[Arab|locals]] and black person people.  This requires no [[logic]] or strategy like numbers zero through thirteen, but instead relies solely on aim.  Because of this [[fact]] alone, the game is destined to be a [[Will verb again!|top seller]].

==Gameplay==
[[Image:Residentfalcon.gif|thumb|[[Falcon Punch|How to win at ''Resident Evil 5'']]]]

[[Dead Space]] with shittier controls, no curb stomp and no movement while aiming. The physics engine, leveling up, gore, textures and soundtrack are [[lie|radically different than the fourth game]] since it's much prettier and has co-op. Oh, and a woman with a crazy accent.
    
There are a wide variety of [[Niggers|enemies]] that players will face off against in Resident Evil 5. These include niggers, niggers with axes, niggers with crossbows, niggers with chainsaws, niggers with dynamite, niggers with molotovs, nigger dogs, niggers with rifles, [[Nigga stole my bike|the African version of Hell's Angels]], tribal niggers, fat niggers, skinny niggers, a giant bat, black niggers, Lickers [[Fail|that aren't nearly as bad-ass as they used to be]], a big [[cock|thing]] with black [[tentacle rape|tentacles]] that might as well be a nigger, monsters that pop out of niggers, [[Muslim|sandniggers]], the obligatory final boss who comes back from the dead for the umpteenth time (not a nigger), and niggers.

