==Storyline==
[[Image:Abbos.jpg|thumb|right|Resident Evil 5 summed up in one image]]

[[Image:TRSheva.jpg|thumb|right|[[Rule 34|No exceptions]].]]

You play as Chris Redfield (Mexican), now a member of the [[GNAA|BSAA]](Bull.Shit.Anal.Alliance). He is sent by his chapter's Grand Wizard to Africoon to lynch the loads of black person that the Klan has begun to ship back home (Just because you sent them back to Africa doesn't mean you can't follow and kill them anyway.) Accompanying him is Sheva Alomar, an African whose light skin and [[Brit]]ish accent almost allows her to pass as a human. They fight against a [[kike|greedy businessman named Irving,]] some [[Italy|wop]] bitch named after Microsoft Excel, and [[Horatio Caine|Albert Wesker]] [[Nerd|who obviously watches the Matrix]],just look at the way that fag fights,he dodges bullets,runs fast,wears a trenchcoat and sunglasses, [[pretty cool guy|plans to exterminate mankind for the lulz]] and [[USI|become God]]. In the process, they rescue [[Paris Hilton|Jill Valentine]] ([[wut|who suddenly has long blonde hair]]) all before '''finally''' [[Lie|killing Wesker]] with a rocket launcher (oh yeah, [[spoiler]]). There's some other shit about [[mindfuck|Tricell funding Ouroboros research and people huffing bugs]], but seriously if you were expecting anything more than that, you're probably [[Atlus|a fat nerd]].P

Also the third boss is named [[desu|Ndesu]]

==Controversy==

Not surprisingly, the [[niggers]] are complaining that, since the game will feature [[White People|white]] [[hero|heroes]] shooting black villains, the game is [[racist]] and <s>should not be released</s> Too late. One disgruntled black mother had this to say: {{quote|It's apparently the [[Truth|white character's job to destroy the black people and save humanity]]. This is [[Awesome|problematic]] on so many levels, including the depiction of [[niggers|black people]] as [[niggers|inhuman savages]], the killing of black people by a white man in military clothing, and the fact that [[lie|this video game is marketed to children]] and [[13-year-old boy|young adults]]. Start them young... [[America|fearing, hating, and destroying black people.]]|[[Concerned Mother|An upstanding community member]]}}

This is, however, completely [[Lie|false]], as [[niggers]] are [http://www.dr-tiller.com/George_Tiller inhuman savages] [[IRL]] and it is pretty much every [[white]] guy's job to [[Fact|destroy black people and save humanity]]. Of course, none of these [[Niggers|diverse defenders of civil rights and multiculturalism]] had anything to say when [[fag|Leon S. Kennedy]] was blasting through crowds of [[Spics|rabid Spaniards]] and [[German|Nazi clichés]]. These stupid shitheads seem to forget that the game is made by [[azn|Asian]] people, and [[azn|Asian]] people [[H8|hate]] whites and blacks evenly. To add, the game takes place in [[Africa]], who else do you expect to find more of? Furthermore, the idea that this game will make people start hating blacks is completely unfounded, as [[White|most people]] [[Fact|hate niggers already without the help of a video game]]. It should be also noted that Chris' [[British|English-accented]] [[Interracial|partner]] [[Dat Ass|Sheva]] is black and [[Shit Nobody Cares About|they both team up with the African branch of the squad.]]

Of course - all the concerned single mothers are just having a knee-jerk reaction, as only a [[Jack Thompson|faggot]] would think that people who play video games are completely unable to distinguish between them and [[Second Life|real life]] and therefore believe that [[Grand Theft Auto|stealing cars]], [[Grand Theft Auto|killing prostitutes]], [[Mario|jumping]] on [[I Like Turtles|turtles]], and searching for [[Hookers and Blow|agility orbs]] [[IRL]] is [[serious business]].  Also killing [[niggers]] in the game is one reason its so [[epic]] and full of [[Retarded|win]], [[faggots]].

